Patch Set 2:

Hi Nikhil

I'm a little surprised to see the 12.0.0 release notes on the "unreleased" page, but my reno fu isn't up to providing concrete steps on if/how your setup is wrong.

I suspect it's a bug in reno's history processing :(

Patch Set 2:

The unreleased page uses the "current" branch (whatever is checked out) as the default. That means you'll see everything merged into master, including tags from the previous series.
